Naturally spreading your toes can provide relief from painful bunions, calluses, or swelling. A soft, padded strap doesn't dig into your feet like traditional flip flops so you can wear your sandals all day or on long walks. The cushioned insole features arch support and a firm 1 inch outsole that's built to last. Each pair of Pedi Couture's Pedicure Spa Sandals comes in a handy PVC carry bag so you can store them away while not in use or pack them into your bag. Available in sizes Small through X-Large..
